===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: tài shàng gănyìng piān
===Proper noun===
'''[[太]][[上]][[感應]][[篇]]'''
# Title of a famous [[Daoism|Daoist]] text written in the Song Dynasty -- "Chapters on Action and Response According to the Most High"

